
---

### **3️⃣ CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md**
Create a file named `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md` with this content:

```md
# Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We are dedicated to fostering an open and welcoming environment for all contributors.

## Our Standards
- Be respectful and inclusive.
- Avoid offensive language or behavior.
- Welcome constructive feedback.

## Reporting Issues
If you experience any violations, please report them to the project maintainers.

---
For more details, see the [Contributor Covenant](https://www.contributor-covenant.org/).
